      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of naturally aspirated precision. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that has been fully overhauled for optimal cam timing. Power is routed through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis integrity is flawless, with a reinforced rear subframe and a suspension refreshed with OEM-plus bushings to maintain factory-spec kinematics. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been scrutinized and serviced, ensuring the high-revving power delivery is as sharp as the day it left Regensburg.",
